snippet.title: Replaced Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description: REPLACED showcased it's gorgeous 2.5D platformer style in a new trailer as it took us on a trip through it's dystopian 1980s America world featuring free-flowing combat, a unique story, and distinctive tone.
